<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.10.3">
<l>kalakkiyamā maṉattaṉaḷāyk kaikēci varamvēṇṭa</l>
<l>malakkiyamā maṉattaṉaṉāy maṉṉavaṉu maṟātoḻiya</l>
<l>kulakkumarā kāṭuṟaiyap pōveṉṟuvi ṭaikoṭuppa</l>
<l>vilakkumaṇaṉ taṉṉoṭumaṅ kēkiyatō raṭaiyāḷam.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When Kaikeyī, with a greatly agitated mind, asked for a boon,</l>
<l>[and] the king, with a mind very bewildered,</l>
<l rend="indent">[realizing] he could not refuse,</l>
<l>replied saying, “Noble son, go to dwell in the forest!”</l>
<l>[And] Lakṣmaṇa went there with him.</l>
<l>This is one proof.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
